text: Atelodesmis hirticornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Buquet in 1857. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Atelodesmis hirticornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1857
title: Atelodesmis hirticornis
